# Question 5 — Detect Salary Drop

## Table: EmployeeSalary

| emp_id | month | salary |
| ------ | ----- | ------ |
| 1      | Jan   | 1000   |
| 1      | Feb   | 1200   |
| 1      | Mar   | 900    |

## Task
Return rows where salary dropped compared to previous month.
---
